pizza ( hindi : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is an indian hindi supernatural thriller film directed by akshay akkineni . the film stars akshay oberoi , parvathy &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and dipannita sharma in the lead roles , while arunoday singh , rajesh sharma , omkar das manikpuri and sonali sachdev play supporting roles . the film is a remake of 2012 tamil film , pizza , directed by karthik subbaraj and was released on 18 july 2014 .